venue.name: Wizink Center - Palacio de Deportes de la Comunidad de Madrid (Wizink Center)

tip.text: Exactly the kind of place I want to be for late night tapas and drinks
Do not miss this place. Family owned for 35 yrs, awesome staff, delicious couscous for cheap and great Tunisian gateaux as well. Great location too!
Their fresh squeezed OJ is amazing, but pictured is a small!  And a large taken 15 oranges to make!
